  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A young man was shot in Mattakuli",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Police Media Spokesman Senior Superintendent of Police Advocates Mr. Nihal Talduwa said that two unknown persons who came on a motorcycle shot at a person in Mattakkuliya Aliwatta area yesterday night.",
        "The seriously injured person was admitted to the Colombo National Hospital.",
        "The media spokesperson said that it is suspected that this shooting was done due to disputes between drug and organized criminals.",
        "The injured person is a 26-year-old resident of Mattakulia area."
      ],
